@NODE intro "Introduction"

                            - Introduction -

 You might be asking yourself why? why did we bother to do ANOTHER module
 player? Well, the answer is simple, we couldn't find a decent enough
 player, and decided to do one ourselves.

 The whole concept we tried to base it around, was the fact that it could
 be playing in the background, without any appicons or windows interfering
 in Workbench. This is why we decided to make it a commodity, thus naming
 it Commodity Tracker. Not a very original name I must admit, but that's
 the way it is, so there.

 Please @{ "read on" link copyright} for more info.

@ENDNODE

