@NODE help "ComTracker On-Line help"
@TOC help

 These are the controls for moving around AmigaGuide:-


  '5' - this key on the keypad will allow you to cycle through all the
        gadgets on a section.

  'Enter' - this key on the keypad allows you to go into the selected
            gadget.

  'Help' - This brings up the help section

  'C' - Will take you to the contents page.

  'I' - No use on this document, there isn't an Index.

  'H' - It will bring up this section, the help section.

  'R' - Retraces. Will take you to the previous section.

  '<' - Takes you to the previous section.

  '>' - Takes you to the next section.

  '(' - On the keypad it does the same as '<'.

  ')' - On the keypad it does the same as '>'.

  'Up' - Moves the text display upwards

  'Down' - Moves the text display downwards

  'Left' - Moves the text display left

  'Right' - Moves the text display right
  
@ENDNODE

